Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer for sale this prime +/- 53-acre development site at 190 Day Hill Road. The property is strategically located just off Exit 38, I-91, at the gateway to the Windsor Corporate Park, less than 10 minutes from Bradley International Airport. With direct access to Interstate 91, the site is easily assessable to Springfield, MA (north) and Hartford, CT (south) a 20-minute drive in either direction. The current AG (Agriculture) zoning can support a variety of commercial farming-related uses, including large-scale greenhouse production, or solar farm. The size and superior location of the property make it a strong candidate for rezoning to accommodate multiple higher forms of commercial development, including apartments, retail, office, and medical as well as various industrial uses  warehouse/distribution, manufacturing, and R & D.

Other properties in the area that I represent: 105 Baker Hollow Road and 903 Day Hill Road are currently under contract.
